rComments: He's a good instructor, very approachable outside class and tries hard to help students. Assignments: he gave plenty of help and tips on the discussion board, high average. There were no past midterms so he gave us practice questions for the midterm, also high average. No practice at all for final, super hard. My average dropped by 14% after.

his STA303 is really tough.  Dont know if he will take over 303 in the future, but if you do have a choice, either another prof or course, DO NOT take it with him. The assignments are heavy loaded and extremely difficult. Badass. If some of you might take 303 with Jeff, okay, praying for you. Try STAC50, STAC51, and STAC32 in UTSC.
The best stat prof at uoft. Makes funny jokes. Straight forward test, assignment.
